{"Body":"<p>I wonder which variant of reconstruction of this word, meaning \"sheep\" in PIE is the correct.</p>\n\n<p>Beekes gives <strong>*<em>h₃eu̯is</em></strong>, Fortson gives <strong>*<em>h₂ou̯is</em></strong>. Both are respected scholars, Fortson's source is the later. Who is correct?</p>\n", "Id":"2175", "LastEditorUserId":"624", "Title":"h₂ou̯is or h₃eu̯is", "CreationDate":"2012-06-25T00:01:11.667", "OwnerUserId":"624", "PostTypeId":"1", "Tags":"<proto-indo-european>", "AnswerCount":"0", "comments":[], "LastEditDate":"2012-09-21T15:53:03.350", "LastEditedUser":{"UpVotes":"81", "DownVotes":"60", "Id":"624", "AccountId":"407237", "Views":"34", "Reputation":"1743", "CreationDate":"2011-12-28T07:24:31.420", "DisplayName":"Anixx", "LastAccessDate":"2014-01-18T10:33:34.597"}, "ViewCount":"155", "LastActivityDate":"2012-09-21T15:53:03.350", "Score":"2", "CommentCount":"16", "OwnerUser":{"UpVotes":"81", "DownVotes":"60", "Id":"624", "AccountId":"407237", "Views":"34", "Reputation":"1743", "CreationDate":"2011-12-28T07:24:31.420", "DisplayName":"Anixx", "LastAccessDate":"2014-01-18T10:33:34.597"}}